item.title: CVE-2022-2144|2024-08-03T00:24:44.277Z -- unknown -- jquery%20validation%20for%20contact%20form%207
item.description: The Jquery Validation For Contact Form 7 WordPress plugin before 5.3 does not have CSRF check in place when updating its settings, which could allow attackers to make a logged in admin change Blog options like default_role, users_can_register via a CSRF attack
